1.0.0.name: wordpress/user-agent-theme-switcher
1.0.0.description:
UserAgent Theme Switcher is a simple plugin which lets you change the theme to be displayed according to the detected browser.

Checks from a predefined list useragent so that the user can at will change the theme shown for that browser. A user can configure a special theme for example for mobile phones that is lighter and this adapted to these devices

Ideal for displaying themes ready to opera mobile, internet explorer mobile, iphone, android, etc.

Now the cache is not supported but will work so that if it is supported in the future
